---
import BlockQuote from "@/components/ui/BlockQuote.astro";
import MeshtasticLogo from "@/images/meshtastic.svg";
import Layout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="CB's Mesh"
  description="Mesh around and find out...">
  <p class="text-2xl">
    This is a tiny website with information about my <a
      href="https://meshtastic.org/">Meshtastic</a
    > setup in Philly.
  </p>
  <p>What is meshtastic?</p>
  <BlockQuote className="flex flex-col items-start gap-3 md:flex-row md:items-center">
    <div>
      <MeshtasticLogo class="max-h-24 w-auto flex-shrink" />
    </div>
    <div>
      Meshtastic is a project that enables you to use inexpensive LoRa radios as
      a long range off-grid communication platform in areas without existing or
      reliable communications infrastructure. This project is 100% community
      driven and open source!
    </div>
  </BlockQuote>
  <p>
    I'm connected to <a href="https://phillymesh.net/">Philly Mesh!</a> They run
    several Meshtastic nodes in the Greater Philadelphia area. They also run <a
      href="https://discord.gg/MWWbAkRR9v">an excellent Discord server.</a
    > You should join it and chat with other nerds like me!
  </p>
</Layout>

<style>
  @reference "tailwindcss";

  p {
    padding: 1rem 0;
  }
  a {
    @apply after:content-[ "_â†—"];
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
